{"_id":"post-7484b8f3-ccf1-4993-8c81-5ecd2f936545","_type":"post","title":"Announcing Kajam 2022! Here's how to get started...","slug":{"_type":"slug","current":"announcing-kajam-2022"},"body":[{"_key":"3115f9499a70","children":[{"_type":"span","marks":[],"text":"We are stoked to announce Kajam 2022 - Replit's second annual game jam! If you're interested in registering head right on over to the official ","_key":"3115f9499a700"},{"_type":"span","marks":["d96e873c89bd"],"text":"Kajam site","_key":"3115f9499a701"},{"_type":"span","marks":[],"text":".","_key":"3115f9499a702"}],"markDefs":[{"_key":"d96e873c89bd","_type":"link","href":"https://kajam.replit.com/"}],"_type":"block","style":"normal"},{"_key":"1f3909816841","children":[{"_type":"span","marks":[],"text":"This year, we're leveling everything up - including the prizes. The total prize pool is over $35,000 and will be split up amongst 7 different prizes. Kajam registrants will have 7 days to hack together the best dang game they can dream up.","_key":"1f39098168410"}],"markDefs":[],"_type":"block","style":"normal"},{"_key":"29a62cda1e24","children":[{"_type":"span","marks":[],"text":"How do I participate?","_key":"29a62cda1e240"}],"markDefs":[],"_type":"block","style":"h2"},{"_key":"1d3287a41eb4","children":[{"_type":"span","marks":[],"text":"To start off, you'll need to register for Kajam which you can do ","_key":"1d3287a41eb40"},{"_type":"span","marks":["19a8cd13f4de"],"text":"here","_key":"1d3287a41eb41"},{"_type":"span","marks":[],"text":". Kajam will officially take place from June 25th to July 2nd. Once you're done with the final touches on your game, you'll need to make sure it's submitted.","_key":"1d3287a41eb42"}],"markDefs":[{"_key":"19a8cd13f4de","_type":"link","href":"https://kajam.replit.com/"}],"_type":"block","style":"normal"},{"_key":"35821396d885","children":[{"_type":"span","marks":[],"text":"To submit your game, you'll need to do two things. First, post the repl of your game to replit.com/community with the hashtag #Kajam2022. Once posted, you'll also need to submit your game through the submission form on the official ","_key":"35821396d8850"},{"_type":"span","marks":["5c89476229c9"],"text":"jam site","_key":"35821396d8851"},{"_type":"span","marks":[],"text":". Your game must be submitted by 11:59 PM PST on July 2, 2022.","_key":"35821396d8852"}],"markDefs":[{"_key":"5c89476229c9","_type":"link","href":"https://kajam.replit.com/"}],"_type":"block","style":"normal"},{"_key":"b5a3884a7b19","children":[{"_type":"span","marks":[],"text":"When the hackathon ends and all games are submitted, we'll give the judges 3 days to choose winners. The judges will be choosing winners based on the prize categories listed on the ","_key":"b5a3884a7b190"},{"_type":"span","marks":["4f6852e712cb"],"text":"jam site","_key":"b5a3884a7b191"},{"_type":"span","marks":[],"text":". Be sure to tune in to our closing ceremony livestream on ","_key":"b5a3884a7b192"},{"_type":"span","marks":["67a2e4783802"],"text":"YouTube","_key":"b5a3884a7b193"},{"_type":"span","marks":[],"text":" on July 9 to hear us announce the winners live!","_key":"b5a3884a7b194"}],"markDefs":[{"_key":"4f6852e712cb","_type":"link","href":"https://kajam.replit.com/"},{"_key":"67a2e4783802","_type":"link","href":"https://www.youtube.com/replityt"}],"_type":"block","style":"normal"},{"_key":"40ab9fbf3b7f","children":[{"_type":"span","marks":[],"text":"Resources to Get Started","_key":"40ab9fbf3b7f0"}],"markDefs":[],"_type":"block","style":"h2"},{"_key":"f1c1962c63a6","children":[{"_type":"span","marks":[],"text":"Kajam is the perfect hackathon for beginners and experts alike, but we also know jumping into coding can feel intimidating. That's why we've gathered up a whole bundle of resources to help you get started. Want to build Mario or Zelda in an hour? We've got dedicated videos below to show you how - step by step. Check out the resources below for everything from official docs to one off repls you can fork and remix for inspiration.","_key":"f1c1962c63a60"}],"markDefs":[],"_type":"block","style":"normal"},{"_key":"2a34b5e8cfd8","children":[{"_type":"span","marks":[],"text":"Kaboom Docs","_key":"2a34b5e8cfd80"}],"markDefs":[],"_type":"block","style":"h2"},{"_key":"08891afe2e5e","children":[{"_type":"span","marks":["c462dc64f2d6"],"text":"Kaboom Official Docs","_key":"08891afe2e5e0"}],"markDefs":[{"_key":"c462dc64f2d6","_type":"link","href":"https://kaboomjs.com"}],"_type":"block","style":"normal","level":1,"listItem":"bullet"},{"_key":"1f066708a77d","children":[{"_type":"span","marks":["b35f76624f85"],"text":"Kaboom Playground","_key":"1f066708a77d0"}],"markDefs":[{"_key":"b35f76624f85","_type":"link","href":"https://kaboomjs.com/play?demo=add"}],"_type":"block","style":"normal","level":1,"listItem":"bullet"},{"_key":"7600e6562bc4","children":[{"_type":"span","marks":[],"text":"Kaboom Templates","_key":"7600e6562bc40"}],"markDefs":[],"_type":"block","style":"h2"},{"_key":"a3d0d003acb3","children":[{"_type":"span","marks":["ac01dd40d814"],"text":"Kaboom Template","_key":"a3d0d003acb30"}],"markDefs":[{"_key":"ac01dd40d814","_type":"link","href":"https://replit.com/@replit/Kaboom?v=1#README.md"}],"_type":"block","style":"normal","level":1,"listItem":"bullet"},{"_key":"d644d7e640f5","children":[{"_type":"span","marks":["870da0e3e37e"],"text":"Kaboom Platformer Template","_key":"d644d7e640f50"}],"markDefs":[{"_key":"870da0e3e37e","_type":"link","href":"https://replit.com/@slmjkdbtl/Kaboom-Platformer?v=1"}],"_type":"block","style":"normal","level":1,"listItem":"bullet"},{"_key":"3da73bc2fb2b","children":[{"_type":"span","marks":["e0484b796b9c"],"text":"Kaboom Typescript Template","_key":"3da73bc2fb2b0"}],"markDefs":[{"_key":"e0484b796b9c","_type":"link","href":"https://replit.com/@NassimSaboundj1/Kaboom-TypeScript?v=1#readme.md"}],"_type":"block","style":"normal","level":1,"listItem":"bullet"},{"_key":"ec76a7ff1896","children":[{"_type":"span","marks":[],"text":"Written Guide